# V3.4 T4: file-based plugin storage writes install
# records, manifest.json, artifact.tgz, signature.txt,
# and the active.txt pointer under this directory at
# runtime. The smoke (T8) and any local `pnpm dev` run
# should not commit the transient artifacts.
.data/plugins/

# V3.4 T5: the dev signing secret is auto-generated
# by `bootstrap.ts` on first boot in dev. It is
# per-checkout (so test data does not leak across
# machines) and must never be committed; production
# sets PLUGIN_SIGNING_SECRET via a real secret store.
.data/dev-signing-secret
